The firm of Ahmednasir Abdikadir & Co recently hosted an Iftar dinner in observance of the holy month of Ramadhan. The function was attended by Muslim lawyers from around the country, including senior lawyers, politicians, civil servants and private practitioners. The main aim was to have a forum where lawyers can engage outside the formalities of day-to-day work environment. The event took place at InterContinental Hotel in Nairobi.